    Method and Description
    io.reactivex.Flowable.dematerialize()
    in 2.2.4; inherently type-unsafe as it overrides the output generic type. Use Flowable.dematerialize(Function) instead.
    io.reactivex.Observable.dematerialize()
    in 2.2.4; inherently type-unsafe as it overrides the output generic type. Use Observable.dematerialize(Function) instead.
